UNIVERSAL VISION said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 21.66% to NT$53,868,000 from NT$68,758,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales             53,868           68,758    
YOY%             -21.66%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            264,205          278,250    
YOY%              -5.05% 
=================================================================
 